	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The NES Four Score uses some kind of ASIC or PAL to emulate some combination of a 74'165, a 74'138, and a 74'153. The Famicom four-players adapter is an entirely passive device.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
